ttps://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a5fb38dc1a69984a16c1b1c007b68172?s=24&d=retro", "bio": null, "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/kgdb00", "tagline": null, "twitter": null, "created": 1616224433, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a5fb38dc1a69984a16c1b1c007b68172?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a5fb38dc1a69984a16c1b1c007b68172?s=24&d=retro", "location": null, "btc": null, "id": 538615}, "last_reply_by": "nanxiaobei", "last_touched": 1635624329, "title": "被 google drive 恶心到了，竟然无法移除存储在共享云端硬盘中的文件", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/811703", "created": 1635565041, "deleted": 0, "content": "一旦点击了“shared drives”类型的共享链接，文件就不能从“shared with me”中删除了，而且还会在“recent”和“suggested”中看到。\r\n\r\nhttps://support.google.com/drive/answer/2375057?hl=en&co=GENIE.Platform%3DDesktop\r\n\r\nhttps://support.google.com/a/thread/10386576/i-can-t-remove-files-shared-with-me-on-google-drive?hl=en\r\n\r\ngoogle 越来越让我失望，从今天开始不再用 google drive ，以后也要慢慢减少使用 google 的产品。", "content_rendered": "<p>一旦点击了“shared drives”类型的共享链接，文件就不能从“shared with me”中删除了，而且还会在“recent”和“suggested”中看到。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://support.google.com/drive/answer/2375057?hl=en&amp;co=GENIE.Platform%3DDesktop\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://support.google.com/drive/answer/2375057?hl=en&amp;co=GENIE.Platform%3DDesktop</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://support.google.com/a/thread/10386576/i-can-t-remove-files-shared-with-me-on-google-drive?hl=en\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://support.google.com/a/thread/10386576/i-can-t-remove-files-shared-with-me-on-google-drive?hl=en</a></p>\n<p>google 越来越让我失望，从今天开始不再用 google drive ，以后也要慢慢减少使用 google 的产品。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1635565041, "replies": 74, "id": 811703}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6512/bd43/11_large.png?m=1620106980", "name": "linux", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6512/bd43/11_normal.png?m=1620106980", "title": "Linux", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/linux", "topics": 6383, "footer": "", "header": "Linux is a Unix-like computer operating system assembled under the model of free and open source software development and distribution.", "title_alternative": "Linux", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6512/bd43/11_mini.png?m=1620106980", "stars": 5631, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 11, "parent_node_name": "os"}, "member": {"username": "guoqiao", "website": "http://blog.guoqiao.me", "github": "guoqiao", "psn": "", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f331/db13/25284_mini.png?m=1440285853", "bio": "a Python DevOps in New Zealand.", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/guoqiao", "tagline": "", "twitter": "guoqiao", "created": 1344839200, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f331/db13/25284_mini.png?m=1440285853", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f331/db13/25284_mini.png?m=1440285853", "location": "Auckland", "btc": "", "id": 25284}, "last_reply_by": "FindHao", "last_touched": 1635622796, "title": "2021 年 10 月，在 Ubuntu Linux 上如何使用微信 ？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/811705", "created": 1635565471, "deleted": 0, "content": "之前一直在 Ubuntu 上用浏览器使用微信网页版。\r\n但是从最近开始（貌似是微信和 WeChat 分家有关？），web 版微信不让登录了。\r\n\r\n我人在海外，由于微信手机号用的国外号码，所以我被分到了 wechat 。\r\n然而，我试了把手机号码换回国内号码，并且微信 app 也明确提示了我从 wechat 转为微信，我依然不能登录网页版。\r\n\r\n因为工作原因我必须使用 Ubuntu ，请问使用微信的最佳姿势是什么？", "content_rendered": "<p>之前一直在 Ubuntu 上用浏览器使用微信网页版。\n但是从最近开始（貌似是微信和 WeChat 分家有关？），web 版微信不让登录了。</p>\n<p>我人在海外，由于微信手机号用的国外号码，所以我被分到了 wechat 。\n然而，我试了把手机号码换回国内号码，并且微信 app 也明确提示了我从 wechat 转为微信，我依然不能登录网页版。</p>\n<p>因为工作原因我必须使用 Ubuntu ，请问使用微信的最佳姿势是什么？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1635565471, "replies": 45, "id": 811705}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1629391393", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1629391393", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 177896, "footer": "", "header": "一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1629391393", "stars": 3342, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"username": "lo0p", "website": null, "github": null, "psn": null, "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/d979abd8f33df8b55a38dce69e985bb1?s=24&d=retro", "bio": null, "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/lo0p", "tagline": null, "twitter": null, "created": 1582175722, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/d979abd8f33df8b55a38dce69e985bb1?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/d979abd8f33df8b55a38dce69e985bb1?s=24&d=retro", "location": null, "btc": null, "id": 470672}, "last_reply_by": "supertiny", "last_touched": 1635622981, "title": "win11 推送了，现在 win11 好用吗？可以更新吗？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/811676", "created": 1635558303, "deleted": 0, "content": "如上题，今天早上过来公司电脑推送 win11 ，状态栏上一直有个更新图标，很烦。", "content_rendered": "<p>如上题，今天早上过来公司电脑推送 win11 ，状态栏上一直有个更新图标，很烦。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1635558303, "replies": 37, "id": 811676}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_large.png?m=1628872984", "name": "share", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_normal.png?m=1628872984", "title": "分享发现", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/share", "topics": 34509, "footer": "", "header": "分享你看到的好玩的，有信息量的，欢迎从这里获取灵感。", "title_alternative": "Share", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_mini.png?m=1628872984", "stars": 4622, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 16, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"username": "fengmenggaokao", "website": null, "github": null, "psn": null, "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/d3ad0ccf02206dc86341d96517fb6514?s=24&d=retro", "bio": null, "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/fengmenggaokao", "tagline": null, "twitter": null, "created": 1419999707, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/d3ad0ccf02206dc86341d96517fb6514?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/d3ad0ccf02206dc86341d96517fb6514?s=24&d=retro", "location": null, "btc": null, "id": 89279}, "last_reply_by": "mschultz", "last_touched": 1635616422, "title": "请各位老哥不要再宣传所谓的 google voice 永久保号了，误人子弟", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/811678", "created": 1635559027, "deleted": 0, "content": "# 网传的 google voice 永久保号步骤\r\n\r\n1. 10 美金购买新号码\r\n2. 20 美金把原来的号码变成 permanent\r\n\r\n# 问题所在\r\n\t\r\n20 美金只是保留你原来的号码所花费的金额，在花费 10 美金购买新的号码后，你的主号码会变成新号码，旧号码不能打电话发短信，并且保留 90 天，如果想要一直保留，需要花费 20 美金。这里永久的意思不是一直持有。只是和原来没有购买新号码一样的保号政策。\r\n\r\n# 补充点\r\n\r\n1. 10 美金只是购买新号码费用，根据你选择号码的所在州不同，会收取一定的税，我自己被收了百分之 20 的税\r\n2. 新买号码不能退款，我和客服 battle 了很大一阵，给我了退费政策 https://support.google.com/voice/answer/7576316?hl=en#zippy=%2Cnon-refundable-requests 注意下面的不可退款的 situation\r\n\r\n# 总结\r\n\r\n花钱只是买新号码，不是永久保号", "content_rendered": "<h1>网传的 google voice 永久保号步骤</h1>\n<ol>\n<li>10 美金购买新号码</li>\n<li>20 美金把原来的号码变成 permanent</li>\n</ol>\n<h1>问题所在</h1>\n<p>20 美金只是保留你原来的号码所花费的金额，在花费 10 美金购买新的号码后，你的主号码会变成新号码，旧号码不能打电话发短信，并且保留 90 天，如果想要一直保留，需要花费 20 美金。这里永久的意思不是一直持有。只是和原来没有购买新号码一样的保号政策。</p>\n<h1>补充点</h1>\n<ol>\n<li>10 美金只是购买新号码费用，根据你选择号码的所在州不同，会收取一定的税，我自己被收了百分之 20 的税</li>\n<li>新买号码不能退款，我和客服 battle 了很大一阵，给我了退费政策 <a href=\"https://support.google.com/voice/answer/7576316?hl=en#zippy=%2Cnon-refundable-requests\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://support.google.com/voice/answer/7576316?hl=en#zippy=%2Cnon-refundable-requests</a> 注意下面的不可退款的 situation</li>\n</ol>\n<h1>总结</h1>\n<p>花钱只是买新号码，不是永久保号</p>\n", "last_modified": 1635559027, "replies": 35, "id": 811678}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d3d9/4468/10_large.png?m=1630643933", "name": "mbp", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d3d9/4468/10_normal.png?m=1630643933", "title": "MacBook Pro", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/mbp", "topics": 7382, "footer": "", "header": "State-of-the-art processors. All-new graphics. Breakthrough high-speed I/O. Three very big leaps forward.", "title_alternative": "MacBook Pro", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d3d9/4468/10_mini.png?m=1630643933", "s